  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objectives of this study are to evaluate the efficacy, safety and tolerability of
      treatment with ledipasvir/sofosbuvir (LDV/SOF) fixed-dose combination (FDC) in
      treatment-naive and treatment-experienced participants with chronic genotype 1 Hepatitis C
      Virus (HCV) infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
